This is the documentation of the API of the Java bindings for GDAL/OGR.

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
org.gdal.gdal
Provides the classes necessary to handle GDAL rasters.
org.gdal.gdalconst
Various constants used by the org.gdal.gdal package.
org.gdal.ogr
Provides the classes necessary to handle OGR vector datasources.
org.gdal.osr
Provides the classes necessary to handle spatial reference systems and transformation between them.

This is the documentation of the API of the Java bindings for GDAL/OGR.

Those bindings apply for GDAL/OGR >= 1.7.0. For previous released versions, some part of the documented API may be missing.

Example programs can be found on the subversion repository.
